Hi Saurav, it sounds like you're having trouble with adding ad credits. To help you out, could you please confirm if you're following these steps to redeem an ad credit?
1. Access the Billing Section.
2. Under Ad Credits, click on ‘Add ad credits.'
3. Choose ‘Customize’ and enter the total value of your gifted ad credit, plus at least $1.
4. Enter the promotional code.
5. Provide credit card information and check out.
If you've followed these steps and still can't add ad credits, please let me know!
Hi Saurav, it looks like you need the ad credit feature enabled first. I'll send an email to our support team to get this sorted for you. You'll receive a confirmation once it's done.

You're welcome, Saurav! If you have any other questions or need further assistance, just let me know. Have a great day!
